                                    1.&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;Make payment for services using your debit MasterCard<br />
                                    2.&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;Pay for more than one item using PayExpressSolution<br />
                                    3.&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;Fill online Application form (form 2), attach your bromide and power of attorney (form 1)<br />
                                    4.&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;Print your acknowledgment online immediately.<br />
                                    5.&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;Publication of your accepted marks are automatic and FREE<br />
